The Dhrystone benchmark firmware.

To build FW simply run build.sh script with parameter EC or IM like this:
>./build.sh EC

EC means Embedded variant, 16 registers, Compressed code allowed.
IM means common RISCV with 32 registers and MUL/DIV instructions.

1) Most probably You may need to edit paths to gcc compiler and python in build.sh script.
2) This project is developed under Windows OS, but to run sh script use Git Bash (https://git-scm.com/install/windows), otherwise simply try to run build.sh in Linux


